[RTEVMS-2278] Implementation (#60550)

* [AI Code] Update "make changes by" date to be delivery_date - 2

- Modified DeliveryInfoDisplay.tsx to calculate cutoff date as delivery date minus 2 days instead of using backend-provided cutoff date
- Addresses JIRA ticket RTEVMS-2278 requirement to update cutoff date from delivery_date - 1 to delivery_date - 2
- Ensures proper timezone handling through existing adjustDateToUTC utility
- Removed unused nextCutOffDate variable to fix ESLint warning

- Use startOfDay() directly on nextCutOffDate to avoid timezone shifting
- Remove adjustDateToUTC() call that was causing dates to shift forward by one day

- Tested across PST, CST, and EST timezones
